{"tid":1856531,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（反共經濟圈）朱凱廸黃之鋒建議台灣若解禁後 先供香港","createTime":"2020-02-01T16:22:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-03T10:21:32.000Z","uid":125168,"like":78,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"f00c31326e0c749e062db6492bd3b5448711312c","tid":1856531,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T16:22:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mwHTCWM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmwHTCWM.jpg&h=863019fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【😷香港口罩不足｜朱凱廸黃之鋒建議台灣若解禁後 先供香港】<br />\n<br />\n現時香港口罩供應極度不足，立法會議員朱凱廸剛剛訪台，建議台灣如果口罩禁令解除，行有餘力可以對外輸出，希望「先香港、再中國」。<br />\n<br />\n雖則黃之鋒未能離境，亦幫忙安排約見台灣民進黨立法院黨團幹事長鄭運鵬，期間<span style=\"color: red;\">鄭運鵬表示：「以人口數和需求數來看，的確合理，我會儘速轉達行政部門。」</span><br />\n<br />\n台灣同香港一樣，都要面對武肺肆虐，大家都去同台灣朋友講聲加油，互相支持下啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/phoenix.cheng.96/posts/10212699161114015\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoenix.cheng.96%2Fposts%2F10212699161114015&d=ANzGKs6Ysw%2B%2BKy1wioRXt7Xqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=75e9e1d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/phoenix.cheng.96/posts/10212699161114015</a><br />\n<br />\n============<br />\n💰支持眾志 <a href=\"http://www.demosisto.hk/donation\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.demosisto.hk%2Fdonation&d=ANzGKs6Ysw%2B%2BKy1wioRXt7Xqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=caac17fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.demosisto.hk/donation</a>"},{"pid":"fa51ae44d62db10fb0a445e725ab4e03dda1e1a6","tid":1856531,"uid":125168,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T16:24:01.000Z","msg":"文宣戰線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多謝下台灣"},{"pid":"5eeb4480c4e89c2f40575e2006f5c2826ce7186d","tid":1856531,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T16:25:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfcdc7d63f7dc19